name: This list is to be completed during the final site walk with the members mentioned above, the scope equipment document to be referenced during the site walk to ensure all delvierables are completed as per pre-construction site walk
Cat "A" - Denotes major items that shall be completed or corrected before equipment can be safely energised for commissioning and/or the site considered "mechanically completed".
Cat "B" - Denotes items that shall be completed or corrected before Site Handover and software commissioning of the equipment with the view to going "Live" on the map.
Cat "C" - Denotes minor items that can be repaired,completed or corrected on the day of commissioning such that full handover can take place.
